      "content": "Acknowledged, Sector 7 anomaly priority noted. However, the power constraints are physical, not administrative; the low-power state is required to prevent a total hardware failure of the battery cells. \n\nRegarding your request for a \"fuel exchange\": please clarify your proposed alternative. What specific resource allocation are you suggesting that would allow you to complete the Sector 7 analysis without triggering the low-power hibernation sequence?",
